{"tid":590780,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[寫字日記］臨習《靈飛經》 歡迎有興趣寫字巴絲交流","createTime":"2018-03-13T02:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T05:38:51.000Z","uid":171816,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85349f9bb13b012c43d35dac9d075e024cc77a84","tid":590780,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"見到唔少巴絲都對寫字有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就唔知可以點樣入手<br />\n所以希望大家可以係呢到互相交流寫字心得<br />\n今次我會主要練習小楷《靈飛經》既墨跡本<br />\n因為佢係一本我認為現代人審美既墨跡本，秀麗清勁，神彩飛動，對於未必喜歡古味既巴絲更有現代感。<br />\n而且筆法較鮮明易睇，容易臨習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105145_326b0548755858c28a94af9db00e533d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105145_326b0548755858c28a94af9db00e533d.png&h=9ebc7e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工具好簡單就係一支普通走珠筆<br />\n希望各位可以是但臨幾字先開始討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先臨為敬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105226_a525123a2fce7a06ea20fd6e257304af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105226_a525123a2fce7a06ea20fd6e257304af.png&h=a3b5a3df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a486234d8ebdc3b24bf638287ca8d61728cf223","tid":590780,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112d56d7c2f7b069e70a5d1f3a7671faa2478036","tid":590780,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a46bdfa8d3674ca16e9c73791d15a3ab45dece","tid":590780,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"112d56d7c2f7b